OL,5, In November 2019, the BBC reported on  
OL,6, Shams Erfan, a 21-year-old Afghan who  
OL,7, fled the Taliban, alone, as a teenager.
OL,8, We met him in Indonesia, where he was  
OL,9, stuck in a refugee camp - one of       
OL,10, millions worldwide with only a tiny    
OL,11, chance of starting a new life. Four    
OL,12, years later, he writes his own story.  
OL,14,FOn the afternoon of 8 November 2021, I 
OL,15,Fsat on the cement stairs inside the    
OL,16,FInternational Ferry Terminal in the    
OL,17,Fcity of Batam, Indonesia. It was a     
OL,18,Fthree-minute walk from the refugee     
OL,19,Fshelter where I lived; an escape from  
OL,20,Fthe camp's small, dark and windowless  
OL,21,Frooms.                                 
